ce:section.ce:para:
Analysis of PL properties showed that gamma irradiation in selected condition induced significant changes in optical properties:

                              •

a less pronounced excitation-depended behavior, emission peak shifts of about 30 nm under the excitation from 300 to 400 nm;


                              •

a small reduction in the bandwidth (FWHM);


                              •

higher intensity of emission bands;


                              •

significantly higher PL QYs.
